t-blue-600` or `text-cyan-500` will replace emerald for the sparkles. The clear button will use `bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-slate-700` with a light border. Also, I will be rendering a dynamic Stats Grid below the greeting card, that uses dynamic data for each tile. Finally, the h-12 footer bar will have a slate-900 background with text-slate-400 color.\n\n\n"
